<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    /* Add CSS styles here */
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f7f7f7;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
    }
    .message {
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #007BFF;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="header">Welcome to Our Platform</h2>
    <p>Dear {{doctorName}},</p>
    <div class="message">
      <p>We are pleased to inform you that your doctor account has been successfully created, and your initial login details are as follows:</p>
      <p><strong>Email: {{doctorEmail}}</strong></p>
      <p><strong>Password: {{initialPassword}}</strong></p>
      <p>You can use these credentials to log in to your account. We recommend changing your password for security reasons after your initial login.</p>
      <p>If you have any questions or need further assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team at {{supportEmail}}.</p>
    </div>
    <p>Thank you for choosing to be a part of our medical team.</p>
    <p>Sincerely,<br>The Team</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
